    org.junit.rules.TestRule

    public class JUnitGuavaEnhancedSoftAssertions
extends org.assertj.core.api.JUnitSoftAssertions
    This class entirely copies the content of the org.assertj.guava.api.Assertions class to make testing easier. All rights to AssertJ-Guava project:

    See https://github.com/joel-costigliola/assertj-guava/blob/master/src/main/java/org/assertj/guava/api/Assertions.java
